2. The 31st day of July 2021 is appointed to be the establishment day for 

the purposes of the Parole Act 2019 (No. 28 of 2019). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

29 July, 2021. 

HEATHER HUMPHREYS, 

Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 3rd August, 2021.
